    {
      "name": "Spellcasting",
      "type": "feat",
      "data": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"2544\" > <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Spellcasting.</span></span> <p>The naga is a 5th-level spellcaster (spell save DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">12</span>, [[/r 1d20+4]] (+4) to hit with spell attacks) that needs only verbal components to cast its spells. Its spellcasting ability is Intelligence, and it has the following wizard spells prepared:</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><ul class=\"rd__list rd__list-hang-notitle\"><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>Cantrips (at will): @spell[mage hand], @spell[minor illusion], @spell[ray of frost]</p></li><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>1st level (4 slots): @spell[charm person], @spell[sleep]</p></li><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>2nd level (3 slots): @spell[detect thoughts], @spell[hold person]</p></li><li class=\"rd__li  rd__li-spell\"><p>3rd level (2 slots): @spell[lightning bolt]</p></li></ul></div><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
